Good Jeff! You are finding a resonance with another researcher. Your contact fields are joining. This is the resonance you read about from the first contacts of the 80&#39;s and 90&#39;s that is so hard to maintain. Its hard to maintain not just because differences in opinion or arguments but also your &quot;paths&quot; may join for only a while and then split as you seek your different destinations (so to speak). 

I write about this like I know because I have shared these same connections with a few select members of this group and we get messages all the time for each other and messages for those they are connected to beyond me. You begin to see depth of the spiritual network. As the bond gets stronger, stranger things may happen so don&#39;t get caught off guard. I&#39;m not talking about scary stuff, just weird stuff that makes you stop in your tracks and think,&quot;Whoa&quot;! LOL

Regards,

Frank R.

