Hi Frank,

You are absolutely right.  I have a woman who works for me who is 
intrigued by all of this.  I started to do a few box sessions with her and 
have great results.  She says she doesn&#39;t hear a lot of things but a lot of 
things she does hear.  And now she says she is a believer.  And once 
she made that statement we reached a different plain of all religious ramblings 
and singing.  This is something new for me but when I am with her doing 
this that is all we get mixed in with messages.  We have gotten some great 
results and then they start singing to us and it is all good 
communication.  Think I will keep her around for more sessions.

Jeff  

